{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-awesome-readme-js","path":"/sublimino/awesome-funny-markov/readme/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Track Awesome List"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"cf4547e5-308b-5edf-8117-961a37bbe8e0","html":"<h1 id=\"awesome-funny-markov-chains-awesome\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#awesome-funny-markov-chains-awesome\" aria-label=\"awesome funny markov chains awesome permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Awesome Funny Markov Chains <a href=\"https://github.com/sindresorhus/awesome\"><img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/sindresorhus/awesome/d7305f38d29fed78fa85652e3a63e154dd8e8829/media/badge.svg\" alt=\"Awesome\"></a></h1>\n<p>A facetiously curated list of delightfully amusing Markov chain output, inspired by <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Memorylessness\">memorylessness</a>.</p>\n<p>If you want to <a href=\"https://github.com/sublimino/awesome-funny-markov/blob/master/contributing.md\">contribute</a> to this list (please do), send a pull request or contact me <a href=\"https://twitter.com/sublimino\">@sublimino</a>.</p>\n<p>Looking for more information on Markov Chains? Try <a href=\"https://github.com/josephmisiti/awesome-machine-learning\">Awesome Machine Learning</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/josephmisiti/awesome-machine-learning\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">50.5k</span></span></a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"table-of-contents\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#table-of-contents\" aria-label=\"table of contents permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Table of Contents</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#web-and-tech\">Web and Tech</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#twitter\">Twitter</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#media\">Media</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#tools\">Tools</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#a-history-of-funny-markov-chains\">A history of funny Markov chains</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#sober-applications\">Sober applications</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"web-and-tech\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#web-and-tech\" aria-label=\"web and tech permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Web and Tech</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.headlinesmasher.com/best/all\">Headline Smasher</a> - Fake headlines created by smashing up real headlines.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.reddit.com/r/subredditsimulator\">Subreddit Simulator</a> - The most confusing subreddit (often on the front page).</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://news.ycombniator.com/\">Alternative Hacker News</a> - Hacker News dataset eats itself.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://lou.wtf/phaker-news/\">Phaker News</a> - Another spin on Hacker News.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.x11r5.com/radio/\">Cybersauce Broadcasting Corporation</a> - A computer generated and dictated podcast.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://java.metagno.me/\">Java! Real or Not?</a> - Guess the Spring Framework class name.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://patchworkdollgames.com/yourswimsuit/\">Your Swimsuit Jumped Over Its Own Weathercock, You Liar!</a> - A dating sim about the futility of dating sims.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://thedoomthatcametopuppet.tumblr.com/\">The Doom That Came to Puppet</a> - Mutations on Puppet documentation and the assorted works of H. P. Lovecraft.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://kingjamesprogramming.tumblr.com/\">King James Programming</a> - Combined King James Bible, Structure and Interpretation of Computer Programs, and some of Eric S. Raymond's writings.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://git-man-page-generator.lokaltog.net/\">Git man page Generator</a> - Suspiciously believeable (but incorrect) Git documentation.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://stackoverflow.blog/2018/01/15/thanks-million-jon-skeet/\">Jon Skeet bot</a> - Stack Overflow's homage to their greatest ever user, Jon Skeet.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://se-simulator.lw1.at/\">StackExchange Simulator</a> - Random question and answers based on the StackOverflow/StackExchange data dumps.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/02sh/4chanMarkovText\">4chan Text Generator</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/02sh/4chanMarkovText\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">24</span></span></a> - With sample inputs for /biz/ /pol/ /b/ /fit/ (NSFW).</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"twitter\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#twitter\" aria-label=\"twitter permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Twitter</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://twitter.com/erowidrecruiter\">@erowidrecruiter</a> - Erowid trip reports and tech recruiter emails.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://twitter.com/TwoHeadlines\">@TwoHeadlines</a> - Takes two headlines about different things and then confuses them.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://twitter.com/SarowidPalinUSA\">@SarowidPalinUSA</a> - Sarah Palin speeches and Erowid trip reports.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://twitter.com/twatterhose\">@twatterhose</a> - A mashup of the Twitter public timeline.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://twitter.com/redditron\">@redditron</a> - Reddit comments.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://twitter.com/markovmtg\">@markovmtg</a> - [Magic] Markov the Gathering.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://twitter.com/nk_markov\">@nk_markov</a> - The glorious leader himself.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://twitter.com/HNTitles\">@HNTitles</a> - HN Titles.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://twitter.com/BeerSnobSays\">@BeerSnobSays</a> - Drunk tweeting nonsensical beer reviews.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://twitter.com/icowid\">@icowid</a> - a markov bot trained on erowid trip reports and ICO whitepapers.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://twitter.com/hipsterwid\">@hipsterwid</a> - An hipster bot trained on Erowid trip reports and Pitchfork's album reviews.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"media\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#media\" aria-label=\"media permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Media</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://joshmillard.com/markov/calvin/\">Calvin and Markov</a> - Calvin and Hobbes strips reimagined.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://joshmillard.com/garkov/\">Garkov</a> - Transcripts of old Garfield strips.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://muldersbigadventure.com/markov/\">Mulder's Big Adventure</a> - Semi-coherent bits of random X-Files dialogue, based on community transcripts.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://joshmillard.com/markov/lebowski/\">The Big Markovski</a> - The Big Lebowski.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://joshmillard.com/markov/christ/\">Jesus Markoving Christ</a> - An incoherent savior for an incoherent age.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://joshmillard.com/markov/sttng/\">Star Trek the Next Generation</a> - Previously, on Next Generation....</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://xkcd.com/210/\">XKCD</a> - 90's Flowchart.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20081224025955/http://www.markovbible.com/\">Markov Bible</a> - The whole book (archive.org).</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://filiph.github.io/markov/\">Automatic Donald Trump</a> - Donald Trump's smart keyboard.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://trump.frost.works/\">Insta-Trump</a> - create a mathematically generated Trump speech.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"tools\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#tools\" aria-label=\"tools permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Tools</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://yes.thatcan.be/my/next/tweet/\">That Can Be My Next Tweet</a> - Generates your future tweets based on the DNA of your existing messages.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.yisongyue.com/shaney/\">Mark V. Shaney at Your Service</a> - Interactie Markov examples.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://mrsharpoblunto.github.io/foswig.js/\">foswig.js</a> - Generate awesome Javascript project names from the popular JavaScript library names on GitHub.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://benedictcumberbatchgenerator.tumblr.com/\">Benedict Cumberbatch Name Generator</a> - Permutations on the gentleman's names.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/Trshant/reimagined-yomama\">Reimagined Yo Mama</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/Trshant/reimagined-yomama\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">1</span></span></a> - yo mama jokes using markov chains (code only).</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"a-history-of-funny-markov-chains\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#a-history-of-funny-markov-chains\" aria-label=\"a history of funny markov chains permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>A history of funny Markov chains</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20011101013348/http://www.sincity.com/penn-n-teller/pcc/shaney.html\">\"I Spent an Interesting Evening Recently with a Grain of Salt\"</a> - The Original Prank (archive.org).</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/19970418070034/http://softway.com.au/people/mvs/\">Mark V. Shaney's Website</a> - Mark V. Shaney's finest hours (archive.org).</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.eblong.com/zarf/markov/\">Fun With Markov Chains</a> - Featuring \"Alice in Elsinore: The Alice books and Hamlet\", and \"The Revelation of St. Alice: The Alice books, and the books of Genesis and Revelation\".</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"sober-applications\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#sober-applications\" aria-label=\"sober applications permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.